West States Correlations

In this markdown I will look at each of the features and run correlations on them to see how they relate with poverty proportion. I will also graph out each one of them to get a visual on the relationship.

I am going to first load in the project data that was prepared and then take a look at it.

Look at a plot of poverty compared to new teacher.

project_data %>%
  ggplot(aes(New_Teachers_Proportion, Poverty_Proportion)) + 
  geom_point()

I am going to look at the correlation for new teachers.

cor.test(project_data$New_Teachers_Proportion, project_data$Poverty_Proportion)
